    "plain_content":  "Email not displaying correctly? View it in your browser ( {{Weblink}} ).\n\nStart your fitness journey today!\n\nYou’ll find classes and workouts for every fitness level. Our friendly instructors are here to help you find the right programs to achieve your workout goals.\n\nCheck out our class schedule and get know the instructors!\n\nClass Schedule\n\nBrowse some of our most popular classes!\n\n*Yoga*\n\nBoost your wellbeing with stretches and poses that are rooted in ancient tradition. Focus on flexibility and strength while you learn to control your breathing. It’s one of our most popular classes!\n\n*Hip Hop Dance*\n\nThis high-energy dance class is guaranteed to get your heart rate up. Led by our award-winning instructor, Lisa Williams, former back-up dancer for Destiny\u0027s Child.\n\n*Crossfit*\n\nLearn how to lift weights the right way with this high-intensity workout. These quick-hitting classes change daily to provide variety in your fitness routine. Join us for an introductory class to give it a try!\n\nNo yearly fees. No commitments.\nPay monthly or buy a series of classes.\n\nPayment Plans\n\n*FACEBOOK* ( http://h )\n\n*T* ( http://h ) *WITTER*\n\n*Y* ( http://h ) *OUTUBE*\n\n*T* ( http://h ) *ERMS*\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://sendgrid.com/ )",
